{"tid":918091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英偵探指迫拍片上電視認罪　促政府撤銷牌照將央視逐出英國","createTime":"2018-11-27T02:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T02:29:05.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e62b028a2ceb471073b854414d7d2523ac21613e","tid":918091,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T02:29:05.000Z","msg":"曾在中國被囚禁的英國偵探韓飛龍（Peter Humphrey），指控中國官方中央電視台，與中國警方合作製作播放他被迫認罪的片段，質疑央視違反英國廣播規定，要求英國廣播管理機構英國通訊辦公廳（Ofcom），撤銷央視在英國的播放牌照。<br />\n<br />\n韓飛龍與美籍華人妻子虞英曾(Yu Yingzeng)，曾受藥廠葛蘭素史克委託，調查藥廠中國高層行賄等醜聞，2014年被上海法院判非法獲取公民訊息罪成入獄，到2015年6月被驅逐出境。<br />\n<br />\n韓飛龍上星期五向Ofcom投訴，指央視在他受審之前，就和警方合作，錄製播放他被迫講的認罪片段，片段在央視國際頻道中國環球電視網(CGTN)播放，在英國的英語頻道都有播放。<br />\n<br />\nOfcom 發言人回應指，已收到投訴，若調查發現有違反英國廣播規定會執法，Ofcom有權懲罰違反規定的廣播機構，包括罰款甚至吊銷牌照。央視未有回應報道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E8%8B%B1%E5%81%B5%E6%8E%A2%E6%8C%87%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%92%AD%E8%A2%AB%E8%BF%AB%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA%E7%89%87-%E4%BF%83%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%92%A4%E9%8A%B7%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E7%89%8C%E7%85%A7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%2581%25B5%25E6%258E%25A2%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E9%2585%258D%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2592%25AD%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25BF%25AB%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E7%2589%2587-%25E4%25BF%2583%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2592%25A4%25E9%258A%25B7%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E7%2589%258C%25E7%2585%25A7%2F&d=JGgYy0LqdrBMYXb44KbCrozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=a94e9338\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%2581%25B5%25E6%258E%25A2%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E9%2585%258D%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2592%25AD%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25BF%25AB%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E7%2589%2587-%25E4%25BF%2583%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2592%25A4%25E9%258A%25B7%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E7%2589%258C%25E7%2585%25A7%2F&h=c30cefc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E8%8B%B1%E5%81%B5%E6%8E%A2%E6%8C%87%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E6%92%AD%E8%A2%AB%E8%BF%AB%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA%E7%89%87-%E4%BF%83%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%92%A4%E9%8A%B7%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E7%89%8C%E7%85%A7/</a>"}]}